Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.001\fs75\c&H0521D2&\3c&HEAE9C3&\4c&H38B04E&\bord5\shad8\pos(760,870)\fad(900,0)}Here Comes the High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you seen it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Those two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Overflowing with startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.31,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishō Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.07,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way, you there, \Nhere comes Benio! {reference to  "そこのけそこのけお馬が通る"}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She comes to confront the despised Lieutenant Colonel Innen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the Lt Col himself only has Buddha to rely on \Nas he holds onto that bathroom stall door for dear life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this weakling be in the military?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, without realizing it, Benio meets \Nthe division commander and explains the situation to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the man with a big heart he is, \NLieutenant General Okouchi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is saddened to inform them that once an order is enacted, there's no taking it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's finally time to say goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,their hearts become one for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio swore to herself that, \Nonce Shinobu comes back alive and well,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,she will be his wife for good. \NBut until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,alas, the cruel destiny \Ndecided to split their paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I have to learn to behave \Nlike a proper woman before Shinobu returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realise I was in your way.\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I need to behave myself from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,!oohaY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this wrong as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:30.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEAE3EB&\blur1.001\bord0\pos(706,161)}Episode 26 \N{\fs70.001}Behave Like a Woman and Quit Drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This mansion feels empty without Young Master, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's worse, there's something wrong with Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, \Nbut she's been acting eerily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's just like me! {not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:48.90,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she ate something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:04:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that is just how a woman \Nin love for the first time acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a passionate romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go men-hunting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tea... c-calms your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And is a true... cure-all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,An impatient apprentice \Nnever becomes a master. {no clue what she means tbh}{/Hasty preparation always comes to light.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A flower is able to project its own arranger's heart in its purest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Lady Benio, follow your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, I'll do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished. Not too shabby if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you stop making fools of other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I do it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to be feminine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shinobu returns, \NI have to be a changed woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Still,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I told him how I feel, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't bring myself to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to confess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Done and dusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Boss, where are we goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, at least say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Special edition!\NSpecial edition, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? How unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Special edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Only five sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm suffering here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet you're out here, \Ntrying to profit from a serious matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rude! So rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.75,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I get it! I get it, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:08.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,600)\c&H2E2F30&\3c&HD0D1CA&\blur1.001}The Imperial Army goes to Siberia to help the Czechoslovak Legion!\NAfter the 5th Division, the 13th Kokura Division is to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! The 13th Kokura Division—\Nisn't it Shinobu's?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:13.41,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,2000)\c&H0F0512&\blur1.001\3c&H4027AA&}Departure on August 13th
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,August 13th...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They've boarded the ship already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Siberia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu went to Siberia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:08:09.56,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Hail Mary, full of grace, the Lord is with you {Богородице Дево, радуйся, Благодатная Марие, Господь с Тобою}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In August 1918,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,troops were dispatched from all over the world, including Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to help their ex-allies  \Nin the revolutionary civil war in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That would mark the beginning of a protracted war of intervention that would last four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,take care of Grandfather and Grandmother while I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only them, but also Tenmaru and Chimaru. \NThey wouldn't accept food from anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor me... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault that they sent you to Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they're sending you \Nto the Siberian battlefields too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Siberia is a cold place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Full of dangerous animals like wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine?\NWon't you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen \Ndefinitely knew all about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew that the Kokura division \Nwould go to Siberia next,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so he purposely transferred Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a gutless excuse for a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, this isn't the time to weep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you going out, Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He sent my Shinobu to that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen, \Nwe'll talk face to face now! {/you won't get away with it}{nc whats this dankokkogira}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:25.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H232530&\3c&H445770&}Imperial Army First Division
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't try to stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have a talk with the Division Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry, but we don't have the authority \Nto address him directly... {not sure what's "taking no notice (of); thinking nothing of" here, maybe it's about benio}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No excuses! Get me to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hanamura Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her I'm away. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare pretend you're not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I didn't mean to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, coffee or cocoa, which one do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with cocoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind! I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to buy me off with food and drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me meet Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me meet him! \NLet me meet him! Let me meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen's not here, uh-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then make him come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't do that either, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been transferred to Manchuria, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To Manchuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was he transferred?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, uh, on top of the Ijuuin case, you know, there were many rumors about him, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is why he's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your uh-huh-huhing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the only thing the Imperial Army is good for? \NUh-huh-uh? Oh-huh-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However... uh... even if I do something... well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Too wishy-washy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, uh, if anything happens to Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh, well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, but like, you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE7E8E5&\3c&H1D2336&\bord1.999\blur1.001\fs200\frz348.6\pos(852.001,115.001)}Slimy{damply; moistly; clammily; stickily}{nc what it refers to here}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh! Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit mimicking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huhing and oh-hoing is my shtick! {/bad habit/filler words}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! I've unconsciously started to do the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:53.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Can't you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However... well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye-aye! Uh-uh-uh! Aye-aye-aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't talk entirely in that! {nc what he means by "but if you make it in time/make do/manage with it, it won't do"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... Oh-ho! Uh-uh... Aye-aye! \NUh-uh... Aye-aye-aye! {I need to go catch a break, preferably somewher in a mountain recluse for half a year at least - perevodildo; me too - alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant General!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I bit my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun, though.\NI still need someone to vent my anger on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So anticlimactic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can have fun while I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:50.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HAE81DA&\3c&H56D1EB&\blur1.001\fs100.001\frz327.7\pos(1121,82.001)}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done to deserve this hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster! Demon! {The original translation was so loose even I could tell.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I hate you? \NYou're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise everything alcohol-related!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look: this is the face you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so rude? You know how much \Nof a narcissist I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what can I do? \NBlame alcohol, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss! I got myself some good one! \NWanna have a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to make me relapse! {good one}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess she doesn't need to be drunk to be violent. {/she's a brawler even without drinking}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't sit still right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Young Lady.\NYoung Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You could make a tea vow or a salt vow.{\i0} {doesn't make sense but literal and idk how else this could be played out}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? A tea or salt vow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, you make a wish to the gods \Nand in exchange,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you sacrifice your strongest food habit. \NStop consuming that thing completely.{\i0} {/your favorite dish}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you were still a baby yourself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you got a serious case of measles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, since your mother truly loved tea,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she swore to the gods that she would abstain from drinking it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and asked them to help you recover. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a tea vow because you can't drink tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. Back in the day, people used do to this for their loved ones,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}metaphorically sacrificing for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? A headstand?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:49.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H161618&\3c&HE0E0E1&\pos(840,541)}Abstinence {禁酒}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not headstand, but abstain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll quit drinking. Once and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,God, Buddha, I beg you.{she says お祈り様 - something like "I beg you - here's a prayer for you" is my takeaway}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H161618&\3c&HE0E0E1&\frz346\pos(909,57)}Abstinence {禁酒}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please protect Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:11.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H161618&\fs30\3c&HE0E0E1&\pos(712,146)}Abstinence {禁酒}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for your kindness, I will try to abstain from drinking alcohol with all my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu... this is all I can do for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To our brave heroes, banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, Benio!\NBenio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, there's a huge lantern procession outside! Wanna see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wishing our army success in Russia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Lantern procession?\NI'm not interested in that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Now that's rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she didn't know what was going on, \Nshe would always go and steal someone's lantern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai! Dunno what this is for, \Nbut all the best to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But now she's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, wake up! You're going to miss the lantern procession!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Buzz off! {"Piss off" is unnecessarily vulgar.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.11,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Go away! I told you I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, the Count wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good thing you've come.\NHere's to our army's ultimate victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd wanna join too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sweet potato shochu sent from Count's homeland - Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you drink, you do it with this kind of cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is a special day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Help yourself, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, a-actually..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way you'll refuse a drink. \NI know you too well. Now, bottoms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're drinking to Shinobu's safety.\NAt least take a sip if you don't want all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying you don't want to drink to Shinobu's safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I would never! \NIt's unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you vacillating and not drinking, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tea vow and the salt vow come from the innermost part of your soul. It's a sacred promise to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So if you chatter about it to other people, \Nit's not going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, I just can't allow myself to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Does this sake taste worse to you somehow \Nif it's for Shinobu's safety?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, don't take it personally \Nover a mere cup of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll excuse myself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Benio. Since you came, \Nyou could at least eat some sushi with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It reeks of alcohol so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As it should be. It is sake sushi, a specialty from Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made with sake instead of vinegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,People who can't hold their liquor \Nget drunk with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In Kagoshima, we always make those \Nfor celebrations and festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It has propitious effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, eat some.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What about some cake, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There's always time for cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon appetit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even this smells of sake, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is savarin—there is always plenty of rum in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rum? I-I can't eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what about some bonbons?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,These are whiskey bonbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whiskey?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't have good things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like Benio to pass up treats...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope no natural disasters happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:42.62,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H352E3B&\fs100\3c&HE0E0E1&\fade(0,2000)\bord0\blur1\pos(720,93)}Abstinence {禁酒}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soldiers this, soldiers that... \NStop boasting it!{\i0}{ep 17, 22:05}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. \NIf only I didn't get drunk that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've loved you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...all this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've chosen to spend my life with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I'm willing to face with you\Nany curveballs fate throws your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. I'm such an idiot! Idiot! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made an irreparable mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, you've got a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to read that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother me while I'm mourning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's from Second Lieutenant, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if it's Shinobu or anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,just let me grieve in peace... {lit: don't ruin the mood - think she means "I'm now grieving for the sake of grieving"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,From Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye. 'Tis right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She was crying until a few moments ago, \Nbut now she's smiling broadly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What will Benio find written \Nin this sudden Pandora's letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Her heart is racing like crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but what awaits her? \NHappy news or a sad notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't wait for that seal to be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:56.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,Next episode preview
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:23:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio opens her first letter from Shinobu,\Nfilled with emotions sent from a far-off land.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, how sweet, yet heartbreaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen \Nkeeps on plotting against Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,fixing him up with some of the most unruly soldiers out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with accepting a fight from another man, \Nbut this is a real battlefield now, in the hostile Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on "Here Comes the High Collar Lady":
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Sunset in Siberia. \NDon't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:21.40,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 27 \NRed Sunset in Siberia
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again{made up to better match song pacing}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings{/This unfulfilled wish is heavy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
